    "title": "BSC Academy is Hiring: Subject Matter Expert (Principal)",
    "description": "BSC Academy invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Subject Matter Expert at our Pimpri-Chinchwad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout BSC Academy:\nBSC Academy is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Content Creation\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BSC Academy!",
